data.description: An amazing value for this beautiful split-level home located in the family-friendly Mount Pisgah Estates Subdivision in Austell! The hardwood entrance foyer welcomes you inside to high ceilings and lots of natural light. Upon entering, you will find an open concept floorplan, incorporating views of the living room with fireplace, dining area & kitchen with a breakfast counter. The master bedroom has vaulted ceilings and walk-in closet with a large master ensuite featuring a separate tub and shower. Double pane windows, luxury vinyl flooring, oversized 2-car garage, recessed lighting & ceiling fans round out the interior. Outside enjoy a deck perfect for entertaining or relaxing. Thank you in advance for showing!
